WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:00.890 --> 00:00:06.340
<i>Many moons have passed since the Imperial 
Army went to war with the Hellhorde.</i>

3
00:00:08.690 --> 00:00:12.570
<i>The royal princess, Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion,</i>

4
00:00:12.570 --> 00:00:17.670
<i>ends up being taken prisoner 
in the midst of fierce battle.</i>

5
00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:24.800
<i>Submitted to all manners of 
torture day in and day out,</i>

6
00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:29.220
<i>she endures these indignities 
without so much as a peep.</i>

7
00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:28.460
<i>Pop</i>

8
00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:29.210
<i>Pop</i>

9
00:00:29.630 --> 00:00:32.340
<i>She reveals not the secrets 
of the Royal Empire.</i>

10
00:00:31.590 --> 00:00:32.340
Dumb Face-o-Meter

11
00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:36.560
<i>Yes, by no means will she speak.</i>

12
00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:39.100
<i>The princess does not give in.</i>

13
00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:41.910
<i>No, she will never give in!</i>

14
00:00:43.570 --> 00:00:48.160
<i>And so, the torture continues 
today, yet again...</i>

15
00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:10.540
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

16
00:02:24.450 --> 00:02:26.960
<i>Torture is away on a business trip,</i>

17
00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:31.260
<i>and with no one in charge, 
the torture is on break for today.</i>

18
00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:34.920
That Evening

19
00:02:39.130 --> 00:02:42.870
Business trips are always a little tiring.

20
00:02:43.700 --> 00:02:46.280
But the moment you change into 
loungewear at the hotel,

21
00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:49.230
and let your body sink into the bed...

22
00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:52.560
It makes everything feel worth it.

23
00:02:53.430 --> 00:02:55.030
Utter bliss.

24
00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.870
I feel like I'm going to fall asleep.

25
00:03:02.870 --> 00:03:04.420
I should eat something.

26
00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:07.330
Ham & Cheese
Burrito

27
00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:11.580
Red Kitsune Udon

28
00:03:06.110 --> 00:03:09.230
<i>Usually, I prepare balanced 
meals for myself.</i>

29
00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:11.580
<i>But today's an exception 
since I'm away on business.</i>

30
00:03:11.870 --> 00:03:14.860
<i>This secluded business hotel room is 
a nice change from my own chamber.</i>

31
00:03:14.860 --> 00:03:17.370
<i>It feels like it's okay 
to let myself go here.</i>

32
00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:21.050
Time to eat.

33
00:03:22.220 --> 00:03:24.720
Ham & Cheese
Burrito

34
00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:24.710
<i>First, this ham and cheese burrito.</i>

35
00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.860
<i>You gently open it...</i>

36
00:03:36.010 --> 00:03:39.650
<i>Then place a jumbo sausage 
inside and wrap it back up.</i>

37
00:03:41.050 --> 00:03:42.530
Done!

38
00:03:42.530 --> 00:03:45.210
A special ham, cheese, and sausage burrito!

39
00:03:58.040 --> 00:03:59.500
<i>Delicious.</i>

40
00:04:01.100 --> 00:04:04.130
<i>It may be delicious, but it's 
not a very refined meal,</i>

41
00:04:04.130 --> 00:04:06.890
<i>so it's hard to tell others about it.</i>

42
00:04:09.770 --> 00:04:12.480
Red Kitsune Udon

43
00:04:10.160 --> 00:04:12.470
<i>Next, this cup udon.</i>

44
00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:21.770
<i>Lately, I enjoy keeping the 
lid on for a little longer,</i>

45
00:04:21.770 --> 00:04:23.320
<i>so that the noodles end up softer.</i>

46
00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:31.840
<i>Now for the fried tofu.</i>

47
00:04:33.810 --> 00:04:36.760
<i>The broth that's soaked into 
the tofu comes pouring out,</i>

48
00:04:36.760 --> 00:04:38.870
<i>and it's a delight just to have in my mouth.</i>

49
00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:41.830
<i>This tiny egg...</i>

50
00:04:42.490 --> 00:04:44.930
<i>It's a mystery how they make it,</i>

51
00:04:44.930 --> 00:04:47.510
<i>but it's tasty and goes 
very well with the broth.</i>

52
00:04:47.820 --> 00:04:52.320
<i>I also have some slightly fancy 
pudding sitting in the fridge today.</i>

53
00:04:55.540 --> 00:04:57.960
<i>Perhaps I went a little overboard.</i>

54
00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:02.820
Torture
enjoyed herself

55
00:05:02.820 --> 00:05:05.070
Breakfast Buffet

56
00:05:02.820 --> 00:05:05.070
Hours of Operation

57
00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:08.700
<i>I ate too much late night.</i>

58
00:05:09.010 --> 00:05:11.670
<i>Let's eat a lot of vegetables for breakfast.</i>

59
00:05:12.470 --> 00:05:15.310
<i>No bread or rice, for a healthy—</i>

60
00:05:14.610 --> 00:05:17.360
Honey butter rolls, fresh from the oven!

61
00:05:21.770 --> 00:05:24.140
<i>I don't have a choice if 
they're fresh from the oven.</i>

62
00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:33.720
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

63
00:05:33.810 --> 00:05:37.100
Sunday

64
00:05:35.340 --> 00:05:37.100
What'd you say?!

65
00:05:37.100 --> 00:05:39.400
His Majesty is injured?!

66
00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:45.610
On Duty This Weekend
Chief Battle Officer
Bruse the Destroyer

67
00:05:39.400 --> 00:05:40.230
Yes...

68
00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:44.690
I hear he's received a minor 
injury to his dominant hand.

69
00:05:45.850 --> 00:05:51.280
His Majesty's defensive magic is 
supposed to nullify all attacks!

70
00:05:51.740 --> 00:05:52.960
Ah!

71
00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:54.630
That reminds me, yesterday...

72
00:05:54.630 --> 00:05:57.720
It was for an instant, but 
I felt His Majesty's mana!

73
00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:59.970
I thought I had imagined it...

74
00:06:00.310 --> 00:06:03.110
but was he engaged in combat with someone?!

75
00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:06.700
Someone who didn't even give him the 
chance to cast a defensive spell?!

76
00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:08.840
M-Most likely...

77
00:06:10.670 --> 00:06:15.590
Who in the world was His Majesty up against?

78
00:06:18.890 --> 00:06:21.810
Saturday,
the Day Prior

79
00:06:21.810 --> 00:06:23.770
Yay!

80
00:06:23.770 --> 00:06:26.450
Today is your first day as a pâtissière!

81
00:06:26.450 --> 00:06:28.340
Let's make cookies!

82
00:06:29.110 --> 00:06:31.410
I hope they end up being good.

83
00:06:31.410 --> 00:06:33.070
It's your first time.

84
00:06:33.070 --> 00:06:35.230
Don't worry about whether 
they turn out well.

85
00:06:35.230 --> 00:06:38.240
The important thing is that you try.

86
00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:41.760
Even if you mess up, don't 
think of it as having failed.

87
00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:44.340
It's the first step to success.

88
00:06:45.710 --> 00:06:48.920
I want everything to go well 
the first time around!

89
00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:48.920
Bam

90
00:06:48.920 --> 00:06:50.170
Bam!

91
00:06:50.170 --> 00:06:51.860
That's fair.

92
00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:53.840
You'll be just fine.

93
00:06:54.270 --> 00:06:56.000
We're here to help you.

94
00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.050
Indeed.

95
00:06:57.050 --> 00:06:59.130
The courage to seek help from others,

96
00:06:59.130 --> 00:07:01.040
another necessary virtue.

97
00:07:02.950 --> 00:07:06.170
Let's start by putting 
the butter in the bowl.

98
00:07:06.170 --> 00:07:07.450
Then what?

99
00:07:07.830 --> 00:07:09.840
We wait about twenty minutes.

100
00:07:09.840 --> 00:07:10.820
What?!

101
00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:13.500
Right now, the butter is still too hard,

102
00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:15.160
so we need to wait for it to melt a bit.

103
00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:16.920
No way!

104
00:07:18.470 --> 00:07:20.180
Geh-heh-heh.

105
00:07:20.590 --> 00:07:22.420
Fear not.

106
00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:29.270
Fire Magic: Demon's Heat!

107
00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:34.690
<i>What?!</i>

108
00:07:35.490 --> 00:07:38.890
That was His Majesty's mana just now!

109
00:07:39.450 --> 00:07:42.750
It's perfectly melted now, 
thanks to infernal heat.

110
00:07:42.750 --> 00:07:43.670
Yay!

111
00:07:43.670 --> 00:07:45.520
Thanks, Papa!

112
00:07:45.850 --> 00:07:48.640
Time to add the powdered mix and eggs.

113
00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:48.650
Cookie
Mix

114
00:07:48.930 --> 00:07:51.970
Maomao-chan, do you know 
how to break an egg?

115
00:07:51.970 --> 00:07:54.620
No, it's still hard for me.

116
00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:57.310
I can break them just fine!

117
00:07:57.310 --> 00:07:58.840
One-handed, at that!

118
00:07:58.490 --> 00:08:02.870
Bam

119
00:07:58.840 --> 00:07:59.450
What?!

120
00:07:59.450 --> 00:08:00.370
With one hand?!

121
00:08:00.370 --> 00:08:01.580
Geh-heh-heh.

122
00:08:01.580 --> 00:08:02.880
It's not a competition.

123
00:08:03.170 --> 00:08:06.140
Let me teach you the simplest way.

124
00:08:06.140 --> 00:08:06.890
Sure!

125
00:08:10.880 --> 00:08:14.240
First, hit the egg against a flat surface.

126
00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:17.100
That'll create a circular crack in the egg.

127
00:08:17.100 --> 00:08:19.580
Latch onto it with your thumb,

128
00:08:20.090 --> 00:08:23.380
then use your index and middle 
fingers to hold the top end...

129
00:08:23.380 --> 00:08:25.450
Now, bend your fingers back!

130
00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:28.600
Magic?!

131
00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.900
It's a skill.

132
00:08:30.150 --> 00:08:33.870
Okay, now add the mix and beat it good!

133
00:08:34.810 --> 00:08:36.720
Then roll it out nice and thin.

134
00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:41.320
Let's cut out the shapes!

135
00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:42.780
Yay!

136
00:08:45.970 --> 00:08:47.480
Geh-heh-heh.

137
00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:48.930
It's a teddy bear.

138
00:08:49.490 --> 00:08:50.580
Huh?

139
00:08:50.580 --> 00:08:52.000
What are you doing?

140
00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.110
You're not using a cookie cutter?

141
00:08:55.490 --> 00:08:58.470
I'm making the biggest cookie in the world!

142
00:08:58.470 --> 00:08:59.480
What?!

143
00:08:59.790 --> 00:09:01.610
<i>What insatiable hunger!</i>

144
00:09:01.610 --> 00:09:03.530
<i>She truly is my progeny.</i>

145
00:09:03.530 --> 00:09:07.710
<i>No, when it comes to cookies, 
she's already surpassed me.</i>

146
00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:10.970
<i>That's my Maomao-chan!</i>

147
00:09:14.420 --> 00:09:16.810
Here, they're done baking!

148
00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:19.080
Yay!

149
00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:20.300
Lemme see!

150
00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:20.300
Ah, wait!

151
00:09:20.300 --> 00:09:21.670
The tray's still hot—

152
00:09:20.300 --> 00:09:22.400
Hurry!

153
00:09:30.370 --> 00:09:32.090
Are you alright?

154
00:09:32.090 --> 00:09:33.960
Y-Yes.

155
00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:35.890
Thank you.

156
00:09:37.160 --> 00:09:38.850
Your hand!

157
00:09:38.850 --> 00:09:40.710
I am the Hell-Lord!

158
00:09:40.710 --> 00:09:43.510
This is but a minor burn for me.

159
00:09:46.420 --> 00:09:48.020
Maomao-chan.

160
00:09:48.020 --> 00:09:51.830
I understand your impatience, 
but you need to be careful.

161
00:09:51.830 --> 00:09:52.990
Yeah.

162
00:09:52.990 --> 00:09:54.500
I'm sorry.

163
00:09:56.500 --> 00:09:58.150
It's all red!

164
00:09:58.150 --> 00:10:00.690
Mama, get the freezy pack!

165
00:10:03.300 --> 00:10:04.250
How's it feel?

166
00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:06.190
All better now.

167
00:10:06.190 --> 00:10:08.020
Geh-heh-heh.

168
00:10:08.020 --> 00:10:11.620
Maomao-chan, you must be the 
best doctor in the world.

169
00:10:13.410 --> 00:10:16.170
Now then, we've made all these cookies.

170
00:10:16.170 --> 00:10:18.880
Let's eat them while they're nice and warm!

171
00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:35.760
The biggest cookie in the 
world is the tastiest, too!

172
00:10:36.270 --> 00:10:38.440
Mine came out just as good!

173
00:10:38.440 --> 00:10:39.900
Geh-heh-heh.

174
00:10:39.900 --> 00:10:42.030
Scrumptious. Absolutely scrumptious.

175
00:10:42.030 --> 00:10:44.240
I'll gobble up every last one!

176
00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:46.290
Ah, don't!

177
00:10:45.020 --> 00:10:47.950
Geh-heh-heh!

178
00:10:48.210 --> 00:10:51.330
Sunday,
Present Time

179
00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:53.980
His Majesty's wound...

180
00:10:53.980 --> 00:10:55.990
Who could be responsible?!

181
00:11:02.770 --> 00:11:05.840
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

182
00:11:09.560 --> 00:11:11.130
But first.

183
00:11:12.330 --> 00:11:15.230
These are a gift from Princess Maomao-chan.

184
00:11:15.230 --> 00:11:17.270
What? Maomao-chan?!

185
00:11:17.630 --> 00:11:19.780
It seems she's made baked 
goods for the first time.

186
00:11:19.780 --> 00:11:20.900
Homemade?!

187
00:11:20.900 --> 00:11:21.950
I'm so happy!

188
00:11:21.950 --> 00:11:23.530
Why don't we open them now 
and eat some together?

189
00:11:23.530 --> 00:11:26.340
No, 'tis the time for torture now.

190
00:11:26.340 --> 00:11:28.890
I must decline such undue acts of intimacy.

191
00:11:28.890 --> 00:11:31.090
But handing over sweets is okay?

192
00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.210
That's right.

193
00:11:33.210 --> 00:11:35.600
Let's save it for after the torture.

194
00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:36.770
Yes.

195
00:11:36.770 --> 00:11:39.280
Once the torture's come to an 
end, we cease to be enemies.

196
00:11:40.060 --> 00:11:42.460
So there's no hard feelings in torture?

197
00:11:43.260 --> 00:11:45.980
Now, as for today's torture...

198
00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:48.690
'Tis tea.

199
00:11:48.690 --> 00:11:49.630
Tea?

200
00:11:49.630 --> 00:11:50.560
Indeed.

201
00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:55.660
Our intelligence has uncovered the 
fact that you're quite fond of tea.

202
00:11:56.510 --> 00:12:00.210
I hear you enjoyed it to the 
point of hosting tea parties.

203
00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:02.490
Tea parties, huh?

204
00:12:02.490 --> 00:12:04.310
That takes me back.

205
00:12:05.260 --> 00:12:09.670
A fun event once or twice a year, where 
I could forget about the battlefield.

206
00:12:10.340 --> 00:12:15.170
It's true that I was a tea-loving 
princess at those parties.

207
00:12:15.850 --> 00:12:17.830
But too bad.

208
00:12:19.240 --> 00:12:21.710
That was nothing more than 
a diplomatic facade!

209
00:12:21.710 --> 00:12:24.730
Actually, I love cola and lemon-lime soda!

210
00:12:24.730 --> 00:12:27.340
That's sad to hear from 
the princess of an empire.

211
00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:33.020
After doing well in my lessons, Jimochi 
would let me have some as an occasional treat.

212
00:12:34.850 --> 00:12:37.410
I just drank tea on social occasions.

213
00:12:37.410 --> 00:12:39.530
I wouldn't say I really liked it...

214
00:12:42.370 --> 00:12:43.620
Hm?

215
00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:45.900
You're warming up the pot first.

216
00:12:46.380 --> 00:12:50.670
Looks like you know the 
proper way to brew tea.

217
00:12:51.420 --> 00:12:57.150
Preparing tea in the proper fashion 
results in a far better taste.

218
00:12:58.220 --> 00:12:59.410
Drool...

219
00:12:59.410 --> 00:13:01.840
I wouldn't mind some tea after so long...

220
00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:02.900
Your Highness?!

221
00:13:02.900 --> 00:13:06.490
Why do you always blab on 
and dig your own grave?!

222
00:13:06.490 --> 00:13:08.090
What are you, a self-driving vehicle?!

223
00:13:09.490 --> 00:13:11.670
How could I let my guard down?!

224
00:13:11.670 --> 00:13:15.160
That said, today I have <i>this</i>!

225
00:13:15.580 --> 00:13:18.430
Maomao-chan's homemade sweets!

226
00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:22.020
You made a grave mistake by 
giving this to me first!

227
00:13:22.020 --> 00:13:25.210
I can cancel out my desire 
for tea with some snacks!

228
00:13:25.500 --> 00:13:28.800
Wow, look at these adorable cookies!

229
00:13:31.830 --> 00:13:33.790
Mmm! They're great!

230
00:13:33.790 --> 00:13:37.710
The joy of this mild sweet 
sensation is filling my mouth!

231
00:13:38.090 --> 00:13:44.600
<i>Munch, munch, munch, munch...</i>

232
00:13:39.700 --> 00:13:42.680
Now I won't succumb to your torture.

233
00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:44.680
A fatal mistake on your part!

234
00:13:45.380 --> 00:13:48.460
Well, ideally, I'd love 
a drink, and a warm...

235
00:13:50.740 --> 00:13:53.640
Warm? Go on.

236
00:13:53.640 --> 00:13:55.110
Y-You fiend!

237
00:13:55.110 --> 00:13:57.380
This was your aim from the very start!

238
00:13:57.380 --> 00:14:00.550
No, you simply brought 
about your own demise.

239
00:14:00.550 --> 00:14:03.230
I wasn't aware of what 
baked goods she had made.

240
00:14:03.230 --> 00:14:05.130
Remain calm, Your Highness!

241
00:14:05.130 --> 00:14:08.200
You're Commander of the 
Imperial Third Legion!

242
00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:11.280
There's no way you'd be bested 
by such weak temptation!

243
00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:12.090
You're right.

244
00:14:12.090 --> 00:14:14.610
I need to remember my days as a knight!

245
00:14:14.610 --> 00:14:18.400
I only drank that tea at parties 
as a way to socialize!

246
00:14:21.150 --> 00:14:22.520
Think back!

247
00:14:22.520 --> 00:14:24.090
Remember!

248
00:14:24.090 --> 00:14:25.970
It's good, isn't it?

249
00:14:26.610 --> 00:14:29.740
Thinking back on it, I really do love tea.

250
00:14:29.740 --> 00:14:30.720
Your Highness?

251
00:14:31.760 --> 00:14:34.520
The princess
confessed

252
00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:40.360
This tea is the perfect palate cleanser,

253
00:14:40.360 --> 00:14:43.240
and it brings out the 
sweetness of the cookies!

254
00:14:43.580 --> 00:14:46.520
I've received cookies from 
Princess Maomao-chan as well.

255
00:14:46.520 --> 00:14:47.880
Let's enjoy them together.

256
00:14:47.880 --> 00:14:49.020
Yay!

257
00:14:49.980 --> 00:14:51.130
What?

258
00:14:51.130 --> 00:14:55.720
There's a mysterious treasure 
buried in the royal cemetery?

259
00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:56.670
Yes.

260
00:14:56.670 --> 00:14:58.330
The princess has told all.

261
00:14:58.810 --> 00:15:03.230
With that treasure, we can penetrate 
the Imperial Army's defensive magic.

262
00:15:03.900 --> 00:15:06.050
Geh-heh-heh.

263
00:15:06.890 --> 00:15:10.220
We can't go defiling graves now.

264
00:15:14.140 --> 00:15:16.970
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

265
00:15:17.810 --> 00:15:21.480
Time for your torture, Princess!

266
00:15:21.820 --> 00:15:23.150
You're...

267
00:15:23.930 --> 00:15:26.980
Don't tell me you've forgotten who I am.

268
00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:28.450
Of course I remember you.

269
00:15:28.450 --> 00:15:29.850
Vanilla Peschutz.

270
00:15:29.850 --> 00:15:30.880
<i>What?!</i>

271
00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:34.250
<i>We only met once, and 
she remembered my name?</i>

272
00:15:34.240 --> 00:15:35.700
Harm-Marshal
Vanilla Peschutz

273
00:15:34.690 --> 00:15:35.700
Hello?

274
00:15:35.700 --> 00:15:37.010
H-Hmph!

275
00:15:37.010 --> 00:15:42.150
Well, I suppose you couldn't forget the 
daughter of the noble House of Peschutz!

276
00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:44.520
Today will be different from last time.

277
00:15:44.520 --> 00:15:46.660
I will have my revenge.

278
00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:51.170
Quake and tremble in fear!

279
00:15:51.700 --> 00:15:53.390
Today's torture is...

280
00:15:54.260 --> 00:15:55.930
Cake!

281
00:15:56.470 --> 00:15:57.380
Oh.

282
00:15:58.660 --> 00:15:59.620
Huh?

283
00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:06.910
<i>And this is no ordinary cake.</i>

284
00:16:06.910 --> 00:16:09.820
<i>Why, it's baked by yours truly!</i>

285
00:16:10.350 --> 00:16:15.190
<i>A homemade cake, courtesy of the high-class 
daughter of the noble House of Peschutz!</i>

286
00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:23.100
<i>I made it all by myself, without 
any help from Mama or Papa.</i>

287
00:16:25.240 --> 00:16:27.050
<i>The moment you learn that it's handmade,</i>

288
00:16:27.050 --> 00:16:30.470
<i>you'll be overcome with emotion 
and burst into tears,</i>

289
00:16:30.470 --> 00:16:31.970
<i>pleading for a bite of this cake.</i>

290
00:16:32.740 --> 00:16:34.900
A cake made by Lady Vanilla herself?

291
00:16:35.350 --> 00:16:37.450
I want some!

292
00:16:38.360 --> 00:16:40.110
Actually, this cake—

293
00:16:39.460 --> 00:16:41.720
What a clumsy-looking cake.

294
00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:42.840
Hey!

295
00:16:43.110 --> 00:16:45.290
The frosting is all messy,

296
00:16:45.290 --> 00:16:47.180
and the cake as a whole is lopsided.

297
00:16:47.700 --> 00:16:50.860
And what's this strange object on top?

298
00:16:51.210 --> 00:16:53.280
A real head-scratcher.

299
00:16:53.600 --> 00:16:55.840
<i>I-It's a penguin!</i>

300
00:16:57.930 --> 00:17:00.350
<i>I-I see, so that's your plan.</i>

301
00:17:00.350 --> 00:17:03.560
<i>Nitpicking at my cake to preempt my attack?</i>

302
00:17:03.960 --> 00:17:06.280
<i>Hmph, how pointless.</i>

303
00:17:06.280 --> 00:17:07.910
<i>Even if it looks a little clumsy,</i>

304
00:17:07.910 --> 00:17:11.250
<i>once she finds out I made it, she's 
bound to bow before its grandeur.</i>

305
00:17:11.590 --> 00:17:13.620
<i>Yes, even if it's clumsy...</i>

306
00:17:13.960 --> 00:17:16.530
<i>She's powerless before its grandeur!</i>

307
00:17:16.530 --> 00:17:18.270
<i>Clumsy or not...</i>

308
00:17:20.990 --> 00:17:23.700
<i>I tried so hard to make it, too...</i>

309
00:17:24.520 --> 00:17:26.140
What are you saying, Ex?

310
00:17:27.920 --> 00:17:31.810
The presentation may be 
a bit clumsy, but look.

311
00:17:31.810 --> 00:17:34.330
The frosting holds its shape well.

312
00:17:34.330 --> 00:17:36.480
That's proof that it's 
been whipped with care.

313
00:17:37.660 --> 00:17:41.020
There's a lot of frosting, which 
was laid on thick with a spatula,

314
00:17:41.280 --> 00:17:44.090
so it ended up looking lopsided as a whole.

315
00:17:44.090 --> 00:17:46.080
But this is no sloppy craftsmanship.

316
00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:49.240
They wanted plenty of that delicious 
frosting to be enjoyed.

317
00:17:49.590 --> 00:17:53.260
I'm sure that was why they kept 
going back with that spatula.

318
00:17:53.570 --> 00:17:57.340
Can't you feel the love of the 
person who made this cake?

319
00:18:01.210 --> 00:18:03.270
And look closely, Ex.

320
00:18:03.710 --> 00:18:05.420
That's not a strange object.

321
00:18:05.940 --> 00:18:07.570
It's an adorable penguin!

322
00:18:08.060 --> 00:18:10.560
Prinshess!

323
00:18:10.870 --> 00:18:13.590
This cake may look really tasty,

324
00:18:13.590 --> 00:18:17.090
but I'm Commander of the 
Imperial Third Legion.

325
00:18:17.090 --> 00:18:20.970
This level of torture isn't 
enough to make me give in!

326
00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:25.590
Huh?!

327
00:18:26.310 --> 00:18:28.000
What's gotten into you?!

328
00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:29.580
Does your tummy hurt?

329
00:18:45.510 --> 00:18:46.560
Nope.

330
00:18:47.190 --> 00:18:49.160
Thanks, Princess.

331
00:18:50.370 --> 00:18:53.430
You don't have to confess, 
so please eat the cake.

332
00:18:53.430 --> 00:18:54.040
Huh?

333
00:18:54.040 --> 00:18:55.030
Why?!

334
00:19:00.750 --> 00:19:02.730
H-How is it?

335
00:19:03.590 --> 00:19:05.990
Mm! It's really good!

336
00:19:07.740 --> 00:19:09.290
You really mean it?!

337
00:19:08.690 --> 00:19:10.020
I'm a sacred blade...

338
00:19:09.290 --> 00:19:10.490
Really!

339
00:19:11.500 --> 00:19:14.710
The cake was
delicious

340
00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:16.270
What?

341
00:19:16.270 --> 00:19:18.950
Two failed tortures in a row?

342
00:19:19.300 --> 00:19:21.460
From Vanilla Peschutz?

343
00:19:21.460 --> 00:19:22.320
Yes.

344
00:19:22.760 --> 00:19:26.070
A harm-marshal failing twice at torture...

345
00:19:26.070 --> 00:19:28.060
It's a disgrace that puts 
our dignity at stake.

346
00:19:28.900 --> 00:19:31.370
I believe that some form 
of action is needed here.

347
00:19:34.730 --> 00:19:36.610
I suppose.

348
00:19:39.140 --> 00:19:44.370
It's times like these that call 
for a good support network.

349
00:21:18.980 --> 00:21:21.520
<i>The Way of the Hell-Lord.</i>

350
00:21:21.870 --> 00:21:24.030
Geh-heh-heh.

351
00:21:24.030 --> 00:21:28.440
<i>I'll get the worst stains off before 
putting the dishes in the dishwasher.</i>

352
00:21:28.440 --> 00:21:30.690
<i>The Way of the Hell-Lord, rule number one:</i>

353
00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:35.820
<i>Take care of the dishes while 
Mama puts Maomao-chan to bed.</i>

354
00:21:37.650 --> 00:21:43.880
Geh-heh-heh.

355
00:21:47.070 --> 00:21:48.260
What?!

356
00:21:50.070 --> 00:21:52.060
She's finally asleep.

357
00:21:52.060 --> 00:21:54.250
I ended up reading to her 
<i>twelve</i> times tonight.

358
00:21:54.250 --> 00:21:55.910
Geh-heh-heh.

359
00:21:55.910 --> 00:21:58.380
Sounds like she was a real bundle of energy.

360
00:21:58.380 --> 00:21:59.750
Well done.

361
00:22:00.810 --> 00:22:02.900
<i>The Way of the Hell-Lord, rule number two:</i>

362
00:22:02.900 --> 00:22:04.790
<i>Evening drinks are always a pleasure.</i>

363
00:22:04.790 --> 00:22:06.620
Geh-heh-heh.

364
00:22:06.620 --> 00:22:08.990
Looks like this is coming up soon.

365
00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:12.310
Pre-School News

366
00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:12.310
This month's event is
the parent-child luncheon!

367
00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:12.310
Please come and enjoy
lunch with your child at school!!

368
00:22:08.990 --> 00:22:11.250
A parent-child luncheon.

369
00:22:11.250 --> 00:22:12.320
Mm-hmm.

370
00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:15.750
One guardian per household can join.

371
00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:20.330
Lulune, you attended on both her 
first and second year, didn't you?

372
00:22:20.330 --> 00:22:22.320
<i>The Way of the Hell-Lord, rule number three:</i>

373
00:22:22.320 --> 00:22:25.920
<i>When alone, call Mama by her first name.</i>

374
00:22:25.920 --> 00:22:27.080
I sure did.

375
00:22:27.080 --> 00:22:29.560
The parent-child luncheon 
is always on a weekday.

376
00:22:29.880 --> 00:22:34.580
You know, we can take paid time off 
whenever we want in the Hellhorde.

377
00:22:41.570 --> 00:22:43.890
Do you want to attend the 
parent-child luncheon?

378
00:22:43.890 --> 00:22:46.740
I <i>do</i> want to attend the 
parent-child luncheon!

379
00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:49.170
<i>The Way of the Hell-Lord, rule number four:</i>

380
00:22:49.170 --> 00:22:51.640
<i>Clearly state any and all opinions.</i>

381
00:22:51.640 --> 00:22:53.640
Parent-Child
Luncheon

382
00:22:57.390 --> 00:22:58.750
Look, Papa!

383
00:22:59.770 --> 00:23:01.330
I'm gonna eat my bell peppers!

384
00:23:01.330 --> 00:23:01.970
What?!

385
00:23:17.380 --> 00:23:18.450
See, told ya!

386
00:23:19.950 --> 00:23:21.610
Geh-heh-heh.

387
00:23:21.900 --> 00:23:22.740
Yes.

388
00:23:22.740 --> 00:23:26.220
You always find a way to 
surprise me, Maomao-chan.

389
00:23:27.260 --> 00:23:40.010
Hellholm Pre-School

390
00:23:27.680 --> 00:23:30.160
There's some more peppers 
left, but you can have them.

391
00:23:30.160 --> 00:23:31.290
Just this once.

392
00:23:31.290 --> 00:23:34.710
What angelic kindness from a demon!

393
00:23:34.610 --> 00:23:39.610
